{"tid":2326477,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓通過《禁散發反北韓傳單法》　脫北者團體擬狀告法院","createTime":"2020-12-15T10:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T10:52:34.000Z","uid":75656,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a4cd9828ffa820089e84807f00efb52c537baf80","tid":2326477,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T10:52:34.000Z","msg":"韓聯社報導，南韓國會14日召開全體會議，在席議員187人以全票贊成通過《禁止散發反北韓傳單法》。<br />\n<br />\n修正案規定，在兩韓軍事分界線一帶散發傳單、對北韓擴音器廣播等違反南北韓領袖達成的協議時，將被處以3年以下有期徒刑或3000萬韓元（約77萬元台幣）以下罰款。<br />\n<br />\n脫北者組團體「 自由北韓運動聯盟」主席透過法律代表指，法例違憲，踐踏言論自由。若政府落實有關法例，將狀告法院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201215/7DAERRFQOZH4JC7BEQOERY37AA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201215%2F7DAERRFQOZH4JC7BEQOERY37AA%2F&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGA7Fv2waV%2FkF2w15sEbuDLw%3D&h=4e9acb32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201215%2F7DAERRFQOZH4JC7BEQOERY37AA%2F&h=0bc69e54\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201215/7DAERRFQOZH4JC7BEQOERY37AA/</a>"}]}